Title: The Temptation of Sarah Jane Smith (2)
Plot: With the Earth devastated under the control of the Trickster, Sarah Jane and Luke go back to 1951 and change things back to how they were- which means that Sarah Jane's parents must die. Will she make that sacrifice?
GuestStars: Yasmin Paige, Ace Bhatti, Mina Anwar, Rosanna Lavelle, Christopher Pizzey, Paul Marc Davis, Jimmy Vee, Georgie Glen, Robert Madge
